### Render template to HTML and plain text
POST http://localhost:50003/render
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "templateId": "test",
  "model": {
    "subject": "Test Subject",
    "text": "This is a test message",
    "test": 200.8
  }
}

### Render template with complex model
POST http://localhost:50003/render
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "templateId": "test_json_node",
  "model": {
    "number": 200.8,
    "string": "Sample text",
    "bool": true,
    "object": {
      "singleString": "Nested string",
      "singleBoolean": false,
      "singleDouble": 99.99,
      "singleInteger": 42,
      "strings": [
        "First",
        "Second",
        "Third"
      ],
      "booleans": [
        true,
        false
      ],
      "doubles": [
        1.5,
        2.5,
        3.5
      ],
      "integers": [
        10,
        20,
        30
      ]
    }
  }
}

### Render template - should return 404 if template not found
POST http://localhost:50003/render
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "templateId": "non-existent-template",
  "model": {
    "test": "value"
  }
}
